high_descs: walk over to the kitchen sink
grab a potato out of the sink
place the potato inside the fridge, and then take it back out
walk the potato over to the kitchen stove
put the potato in the microwave above the kitchen stove and close the door
anns.task_desc: put a cooled potato inside the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and go to the fridge, then go to the sink on your right and face it.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Turn right and carry the potato to the fridge.
Put the potato on the center front of the top fridge shelf and close the fridge door, then open the fridge and take it out again and re-close the door.
Turn right and go to the stove on your left, then turn to face the stove.
Put the potato into the microwave above the stove, then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato into the microwave.

high_descs: Pick up the potato in the sink.
Bring the potato to the fridge.
Chill the potato in the fridge for 7 seconds.
Take that potato to the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the potato in the microwave.
